		<title>10 Employment</title>
		<content>We also made a survey of the Whole area
to find out how many people were       
employed there.                        
Here are the figures-                  
                           MEN  WOMEN  
Gower produce              13    0     
B.P                        1000  20    
Burry Sand Co Ltd          5     0     
Manderwood Eng.            4     0     
S.Wales Sand and Gravel    6     0     
Stillman's Scrap           8     1     
South Wales Wharfage       9     1     
Arc Concrete               4     0     
Argabay Ltd                4     0     
TOTAL                    ============  
                           1053  22    
We can see that by far the biggest     
employers in the area are the B.P      
company.Most of the people working in  
our area live within a five mile       
radius.                                
